LevelCodeDisplayDefinition
1GREG Gregorian The Gregorian calendar is the calendar in effect in most countries of Christian influence since approximately 1582. This calendar superceded the Julian calendar.

concept.definition: The Gregorian calendar is the calendar in effect in most countries of Christian influence since approximately 1582. This calendar superceded the Julian calendar.
